# Local environment files.
# The project-generated .env holds only PUBLIC Lovable Cloud config
# (URL, publishable key, project id, release-control flags) and is
# tracked in Git so fresh runtimes boot without manual restoration.
# Local override variants remain ignored.
.env.local
.env.*.local
